1
00:00:02,433 --> 00:00:07,433
LEARN. Cognitive-development analytics for USMC schoolhouses.

2
00:00:07,435 --> 00:00:12,435
LOGCOM use case: Learning Intelligence Dashboard. Are Marines actually learning?

3
00:00:12,436 --> 00:00:17,436
Eighteen students. Six assignments. Two hundred forum posts. One question.

4
00:00:17,438 --> 00:00:23,438
Synthetic Moodle export streams in. No data movement.

5
00:00:23,444 --> 00:00:29,444
A three-stage agent scores every student against the USMC competency rubric.

6
00:00:29,465 --> 00:00:37,465
A Kamiwaza-deployed model drafts the Instructors Competency Brief.

7
00:00:31,475 --> 00:00:38,475
Three-click drill-down: heatmap to student to remediation recommendation.

8
00:00:38,487 --> 00:00:44,487
Class-level competency map. Top performers. Intervention list.

9
00:00:44,492 --> 00:00:51,492
Every assessment SHA-256 chained. SJA, IG, and TRADOC can replay months later.

10
00:00:51,504 --> 00:00:59,504
Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. FERPA-friendly. IL5 ready. Deploy in hours.
